* To run this in Visual Studio, you'll need to install the Silverlight for Windows Phone Toolkit. Instructions are on this page, under the same title: http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/hh286405(v=vs.92).aspx

* The project uses a reference database, which I build with an independent project. I can commit the 'database helper' project if you need it, but it's not required for the main app to run.
